pan>.<span class=\"name\">TightBindingChain</span>.<span class=\"name\">quantaWaveNumber_exp_N</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">T</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain\">TightBindingChain</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">k</span> : <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain.QuantaWaveNumber\">QuantaWaveNumber</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Complex/Exponential.html#Complex.exp\">Complex.exp</a> (<a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex.I\">Complex.I</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">k</span></span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">n</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain.N\">N</a></span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain.a\">a</a></span></span>)</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain.quantaWaveNumber_exp_N","kind":"theorem","line":419,"name":"CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain.quantaWaveNumber_exp_N","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L419-L435"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain.quantaWaveNumber_subset_brillouinZone\"><span class=\"name\">CondensedMatter</span>.<span class=\"name\">TightBindingChain</span>.<span class=\"name\">quantaWaveNumber_subset_brillouinZone</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">T</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain\">TightBindingChain</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain.QuantaWaveNumber\">QuantaWaveNumber</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#HasSubset.Subset\">⊆</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain.BrillouinZone\">BrillouinZone</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The quantized wavenumbers form a subset of the `BrillouinZone`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain.quantaWaveNumber_subset_brillouinZone","kind":"theorem","line":337,"name":"CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain.quantaWaveNumber_subset_brillouinZone","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L337-L411"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain.QuantaWaveNumber\"><span class=\"name\">CondensedMatter</span>.<span class=\"name\">TightBindingChain</span>.<span class=\"name\">QuantaWaveNumber</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">T</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain\">TightBindingChain</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The wavenumbers associated with the energy eigenstates.\nThis corresponds to the set `2 π / (a N) * (n - ⌊N/2⌋)` for `n : Fin T.N`.\nIt is defined as such so it sits in the Brillouin zone. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain.QuantaWaveNumber","kind":"def","line":325,"name":"CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain.QuantaWaveNumber","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L325-L329"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain.BrillouinZone\"><span class=\"name\">CondensedMatter</span>.<span class=\"name\">TightBindingChain</span>.<span class=\"name\">BrillouinZone</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">T</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingChain\">TightBindingChain</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The Brillouin zone of the tight binding model is `[-π/a, π/a)`.\nThis is the set in which wave functions are uniquely defined. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/CondensedMatter/TightBindingChain/Basic.html#CondensedMatter.TightBindingC